'''Valorum Shipping and Transport''' was a business based on [[Eriadu/Legends|Eriadu]] owned by [[House Valorum/Legends|House Valorum]].<ref name="CoD" /> In addition to shipping and transporting, it also was involved in [[Starship/Legends|starship]] manufacturing and operated [[Eriadu orbital shipyards|shipyards]] in orbit of Eriadu.<ref name="DMS" /> [[Finis Valorum/Legends|Finis Valorum]] was a member of the company's board of directors; this caused a scandal when it was revealed that the company would benefit by his proposal to tax trade routes, and that [[Aurodium/Legends|aurodium]] of the same amount [[Dorvalla Incident|lost]] by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] at [[Dorvalla/Legends|Dorvalla]] had been secretly transferred into its bank account.<ref name="CoD" />

